creator: BabyBus
descriptionHtml:
Search for "BabyBus" for even more free panda games for you to try!

Baby Panda's Art Class is in session!

This is an art classroom designed specifically for children aged 2-5! Games of music, drawing and kids crafts for children to recognize color, learn to draw, sing and dance to music to inspire their interest in the arts.

Baby Panda's Art Classroom includes following mini-games:

DRAWING GAMES
- Fingerprint Drawing: Imprint fingerprint on the screen and watch it turn into a balloon, grape, leaf…Children can create artwork without a pen!
- Creative Artwork: Scribble or tap anywhere on the drawing board to turn doodles into cookies, noodles, dragon fruits and other funny food.
- Coloring Book: Identify crayons of different colors and use them to fill up the blank coloring pages. Learn color patterns and make artwork!

MUSIC GAMES
- Rhythm Training: Listen to the tune, tap notes according to the rhythm and collect stars for higher score!
- Children's Songs: Learn children's song with baby panda and play music with little rabbit!

KIDS CRAFT GAMES
- Modeling Clay: Choose clay of different colors and make noodles, flowers, or crabs out of it with tools.
- Paper Cutting: Cut paper in the shape of a lion, stick it on the wood and you have a fan!
-Necklace Making: Collect bottle caps, decorate them with paint brush and stickers, then string them together!

All art games are free to download, with new exciting updates!

Come to Baby Panda's Art Classroom, and use your imagination to create one-of-a-kind artwork with Baby Panda! BabyBus hopes to inspire children's interest in art during the period when they are most imaginative.

Features:
- 3 major themes with 8 games and 10+ playing modes to fully develop children's artistic talent;
- Brilliant colors and adorable pictures to appeal to kids;
- Easy games for even preschool children to follow and create artwork.

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 250 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have produced more than 150 children's educational games, 700 children's songs, and animations of various themes spanning the arts, health, and science.
—————
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com
